2. Through the interplay of solid and void, the artist creates clear visual layers between the horse-head silhouette and the inner landscape and figure. The zodiac symbol remains recognizable while the internal details invite close viewing. Pink flowers, green grass, and blue clothing form a harmonious palette; the horse tail lines and skin texture are lively and natural, showing solid hand-drawing skills.<br>
