Dear principals and teachers,<br/><br/>
The 3rd Chinese Zodiac Painting Competition, themed for the Year of the Horse, is about to begin. Building on the previous two competitions, this year's event will be improved in many ways. The organizing committee hopes to continue developing this competition as a meaningful tradition for promoting Chinese culture and art. The zodiac painting competition is not only about artistic appreciation; it also carries the symbolism and spirit of Chinese traditional culture. We also hope the competition will provide art schools and classes with a platform to showcase their achievements. Thank you for your support and participation!
To make this year's competition more organized and effective, the organizing committee invites Chinese schools and art schools/classes to serve as partner organizations and promote the event together.<br/>
